h1. connection

h2. Purpose

Set the name of the connection to consume from.

h2. Examples

{code}
def rabbitConfig = [
    queue: "example.queue",
    connection: "local"
]
{code}

h2. Description

The value of this property must match the name of a connection in the configuration.  If no connection name is given, the default connection
will be used, if defined.  If there is no default connection, an exception will be thrown.
